"{\"uid\": \"jamaica-gleaner.com-article-entertainment-20240726-celine-dion-makes-musical-comeback-paris-olympics-eiffel-tower\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) -\\u00a0Celine Dion\\u00a0made a triumphant return Friday with a very public performance: closing out the\\u00a0Paris Olympics' opening ceremony\\u00a0from the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999991315391205, \"rank\": 8.589983355815547e-07, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly two years after revealing her\\u00a0stiff person syndrome diagnosis,\\u00a0Dion belted\\u00a0Edith Piaf's\\u00a0\\\"Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\" (\\\"Hymn to Love\\\") as the finale of the roughly four-hour spectacle.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her appearance had been teased for weeks, but organisers and Dion's representatives had refused to confirm\\u00a0whether she was performing.\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On a page dedicated to\\u00a0Dior's contributions\\u00a0to the opening ceremony, the media guide referred to \\\"a world star, for a purely grandiose, superbly scintillating finale.\\\"\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion had been absent from the stage since 2020, when the coronavirus pandemic forced the postponement of her tour to 2022.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That tour was eventually suspended in the wake of her diagnosis.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rare neurological disorder causes rigid muscles and painful muscle spasms, which were affecting Dion's ability to walk and sing.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, at the premiere of the documentary \\\"I Am: Celine Dion,\\\"\\u00a0she told The Associated Press\\u00a0that returning required therapy, \\\"physically, mentally, emotionally, vocally.\\\"\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9996772485738386, \"rank\": 0.00032285557655161877, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that's why it takes a while.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But absolutely why we are doing this because I am already a little bit back,\\\" she said then.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even before the documentary's release, Dion had taken steps toward a comeback.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In February, she made another surprise appearance,\\u00a0at the Grammy Awards,\\u00a0where she presented the final award of the night to a standing ovation.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow The Gleaner on X, formerly Twitter, and Instagram @JamaicaGleaner and on Facebook @GleanerJamaica.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.9999999999042757, \"rank\": 9.576102846697878e-11, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.894238864077133e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a message on WhatsApp at 1-876-499-0169 or email us atonlinefeedback@gleanerjm.comoreditors@gleanerjm.com.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999999999215561, \"rank\": 7.851376470960374e-11, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"View the discussion thread.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": []}]}"